title: Pixel Buds Pro will be available in these countries, but with limited color choices in some
content:
Google’s upcoming Pixel Buds Pro look like an exciting release from their battery life to the addition of active noise cancellation. Like in years past, though, Google won’t be selling Pixel Buds Pro in every region, and availability of certain colors will be limited in select regions.

description: The Pixel Buds Pro are coming and seem very enticing, so here's what you can expect for availability, pricing, and colors across the globe.
